ub.com%2Fexperiencing-place-in-fiction-on-allowing-your-characters-to-get-lost%2F&title=Experiencing%20Place%20in%20Fiction%3A%20On%20Allowing%20Your%20Characters%20to%20Get%20Lost" target="_blank" title="Click to share on Pocket"><span></span><span class="sharing-screen-reader-text">Click to share on Pocket (Opens in new window)</span></a></li><li class="share-end"></li><li class="share-end"></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div>									
